{"root":{"data":{"text":"四大天王：\n氢、氧、碳、氮","font-size":32},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcay9hc00","created":1531725409572,"text":"氢（H）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-143.74999785795808,"y":1.2499999813735485},"font-size":32,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcef0de04","created":1531725417115,"text":"简介：宇宙中含量高，但在地球大气中含量低，其原因是因为氢太轻了。氢是宇宙的燃料。","background":"#d6e3bc","font-size":18,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcep7pts0","created":1531725417732,"text":"用途：火箭使用液氢与液氧作为燃料发生反应，形成温度极高的蒸汽从喷管喷出，由此产生的爆炸气浪，推动火箭上升","background":"#d6e3bc","font-size":18,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcf2d0944","created":1531725418527,"text":"实验现象：氢气燃烧，发出蓝色火焰，放出热量","background":"#d6e3bc","font-size":18,"layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcbcwynks","created":1531725410458,"text":"氧（O）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-142.49999787658442,"y":-12.499999813735485},"font-size":32,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcg6re8wg","created":1531725420970,"text":"特点：由于出现了生命，导致地球大气中氧气含量增多。氧是地球的助燃剂。","background":"#d6e3bc","font-size":18,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcgkocy88","created":1531725421811,"text":"性质：无色无味的气体，密度比空气略大，不可燃，能助燃，能供给呼吸，不易溶于水;氧气在氧化反应中提供了氧，其具有氧化性","background":"#d6e3bc","font-size":18,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzchpiq6g4","created":1531725424281,"text":"实验现象：带有火星的木条在氧气中能够复燃，说明氧气能支持燃烧","background":"#d6e3bc","font-size":18,"layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcbq52q88","created":1531725411258,"text":"碳（C）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-161.24999759718787,"y":14.999999776482696},"font-size":32,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcig81sg8","created":1531725425896,"text":"特点：人类最早发现并利用的元素之一。化石燃料（煤、石油、天然气）是我们最熟悉的碳的存在形式","font-size":18,"background":"#d6e3bc","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzciu1raos","created":1531725426732,"text":"用途：碳可以形成软软的石墨，用于铅笔芯和焊条，石墨可以导电；碳还可以形成最硬的天然物质——金刚石，用于切割和钻戒。","font-size":18,"background":"#d6e3bc","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcj59ws0s","created":1531725427410,"text":"特点：碳是活体细胞结构的组成成分，碳构成了蛋白质、脂肪、碳水化合物以及DNA双螺旋结构的骨架，没有碳，就没有生命。碳是形成有机物的重要条件。","font-size":18,"background":"#d6e3bc","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcc26hswk","created":1531725411986,"text":"氮（N）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-146.24999782070506,"y":-1.2499999813736622},"layout":null,"font-size":32},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcjwd49sk","created":1531725429048,"text":"特征：","background":"#d6e3bc","layout":null,"font-size":18},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d3o4kzey9i80","created":1724500993044,"text":"用途：","font-size":18,"background":"#d6e3bc"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcks06s8c","created":1531725430962,"text":"实验现象：","background":"#d6e3bc","layout":null,"font-size":18},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}